# 遵循 Conventional Commits 规范
# 格式: type(scope): subject
#
# type 类型:
#   feat     新功能
#   fix      修复bug
#   refactor 代码重构
#   test     测试相关
#   docs     文档更新
#   chore    构建/工具/其他杂项
#
# scope 范围（可选）:
#   bid-parser | bid-writer | bid-review | collusion-analysis
#   knowledge | win-rate | project | auth | export | notify
#   bid-web | bid-mobile | infra | docs
#
# 示例:
#   feat(bid-writer): add three-way routing for section generation
#   fix(auth): resolve JWT token refresh race condition
#   docs(api): update bidding endpoint documentation
#
# 注意：禁止直接向 main/master 分支推送，必须通过 PR + Code Review
#
# ------------------------ >8 ------------------------
# 请勿修改下方分隔线以上的内容作为提交信息
